
<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Account Registration</title>
</head>
<body>
    <p>
        Dear @Raw(Model.FirstName),
    </p>
    <p>
        You have been successfully registered to Swift Financials.
    </p>
    <p>
        Your username is @Raw(Model.Username)
    </p>
    <p>
        Your password is: <strong>@Raw(Model.UserPassword)</strong>
    </p>
    <p>
        Please confirm your account by clicking  <a href=@Raw(Model.CallbackUrl)>here</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
        This is an automatically generated email, please do not reply to this address.
    </p>
    <p>
        @Raw(Model.CompanyDescription)
    </p>
</body>
</html>